snippet.title: Trinity Fusion - Boss Rush Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the Trinity Fusion Boss Rush Beta for free on https://trinity-fusion.com (Steam version)

Take control of your parallel selves on a mission to save the dying multiverse in this rogue-lite action platformer! Explore dark, sci-fi worlds and engage in fast-paced, smooth and precise combat.

View more info on https://store.steampowered.com/app/1911360/Trinity_Fusion
